c=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外就係心齋橋嘅神座拉麵，好鍾意食佢啲菜(應該係娃娃菜)</blockquote><br />\n柚子元當你入到去見你係遊客佢地會同你講 it's not japanese food，千祈唔好比佢大到而掉頭走，我見好多遊客都係咁樣比佢咁講後就掉頭走，間鋪根本唔多願做遊客，剩係做本地都已經忙到仆街，呢間野我去三次京都都要至少要一餐，因為個湯底勁開胃，記得最後要叫個飯做泡飯，呢個真係精華所在。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/171720_18c98927f43f04d10af9ffb077d9f0cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F171720_18c98927f43f04d10af9ffb077d9f0cb.jpg&h=652d0404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/171729_a7f4dc67d3f9c2127a0eb6f182297143.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F171729_a7f4dc67d3f9c2127a0eb6f182297143.jpg&h=471882c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5F8p4uD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5F8p4uD.jpg&h=fd5faab1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"420eda376b28578ea88f9c5ecfafb836e569290e","tid":224633,"uid":70227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:36:54.000Z","msg":"金龍垃圾<br />\n一蘭我覺得幾啱我口味"},{"pid":"fe4b610a3685a9805fcbd53b6d07727447ccf7fb","tid":224633,"uid":41461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81d40400e51a7b1a1e67db3b7026fd872124c84","tid":224633,"uid":23775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊7月又去，巴打有冇咩推介<br />\n之前嗰個post一提金龍就沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己有兩間覺得幾好食<